						<p><hi rend="bold">c. 9th Century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>In Vaṭṭeḻuttu characters. Records an endownment of two <hi rend="italic">kalañju</hi> of gold by some goldsmiths to provide offerings (as <hi rend="italic">avipuṟam</hi>) to the deity <hi rend="italic">(dēvar)</hi> at Ayiraimalai.</p>						

